<item>
            <title>[SOLR-7752] Angular admin UI query pane issues</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7752</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As well as &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7223&quot; title=&quot;Tooltips admin panel get switched midway edismax&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-7223&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-7223&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7737&quot; title=&quot;Query form not highlighting/displaying error responses&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-7737&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-7737&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, the query pane does not accept an &quot;enter&quot; key to submit a form, and it does not parse URL parameters, which it should. Without this, links from the schema browser pane do not work correctly, and queries are forgotten if you reload a page.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
